   <concept id="DAFFARS_5317_170" class="- topic/topic concept/concept ">
      <title class="- topic/title "> 
         <ph class="- topic/ph " props="autonumber">5317.170</ph> General</title>
      <conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody ">
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(a) See <xref format="html"
                  href="https://www.acquisition.gov/daffars/mp5301-federal-acquisition-regulations-system#DAFFARS_MP5301_601"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">MP5301.601(a)(i)</xref>.</p>
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(b) See <xref format="html"
                  href="https://www.acquisition.gov/daffars/mp5301-federal-acquisition-regulations-system#DAFFARS_MP5301_601"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">MP5301.601(a)(i)</xref>.</p>
         <p outputclass="List1" class="- topic/p ">(d)(4) The contracting officer must provide the congressional notification described in <xref format="html"
                  href="https://www.acquisition.gov/dfars/part-217-special-contracting-methods#DFARS-217.170"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">DFARS 217.170(d)(1)</xref>, using the 1279 format in <xref format="html"
                  href="https://www.acquisition.gov/daffars/mp5305-publicizing-contract-actions"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">MP5305.303</xref>, to the <xref format="html"
                  href="https://www.acquisition.gov/daffars/part-5302-definitions-words-and-terms"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">cognizant HCA Workflow</xref> 40 days before the planned contract award date, with an information copy to <xref format="html"
                  href="mailto:SAF.FMBL.Budget-Appropriations.Liaison@us.af.mil"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">SAF/FMBL</xref>,<ph rev="Revised June xx, 2024" class="- topic/ph "> 
               <xref format="html"
                     href="mailto:SAF.LLW.Workflow@us.af.mil"
                     scope="external"
                     class="- topic/xref ">SAF/LLW</xref>
            </ph>, and the SCO. The cognizant HCA will notify the DoD offices listed in <xref format="html"
                  href="https://www.acquisition.gov/dfars/part-217-special-contracting-methods#DFARS-217.170"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">DFARS 217.170(d)(4)</xref>. This congressional notification does not fulfill the requirement to announce contract awards in accordance with <xref format="html"
                  href="https://www.acquisition.gov/far/part-5#FAR_Subpart_5_3"
                  scope="external"
                  class="- topic/xref ">FAR 5.3</xref>, as supplemented.<ph id="Toc38365365" class="- topic/ph "/> 
         </p>
      </conbody>
   </concept>
